				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">While I agree with you that some people cannot equip those pieces at 215, I think it would be unfair to favour higher level ones in the weighted roll.
<br />

<br />
Since we are talking about doing The Beast here and not some level 200 18 hour spawn, the chances that you will get the 1-2 levels needed to equip the item are higher then your chances of the item dropping again anytime soon and you winning then. It's not like we will kill The Beast like every second day from now on. Maybe that will happen once in a while, but I cannot see that in the near future.
<br />

<br />
I'll stop here now since I am drifting off topic, but if you really put those level boni in, then all this will most likely turn into an elitist thing - which would be sad.
<br />

<br />
